{"tid":954754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機場發生咩事?","createTime":"2018-12-24T23:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T00:55:01.000Z","uid":80199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9f4858be6983c81347957517b850625a8fde8234","tid":954754,"uid":80199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T23:07:30.000Z","msg":"見到好多差佬特警又問有無見到可疑人物"},{"pid":"58f30b8356ba80987c9f940ae06335a907d8251a","tid":954754,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T23:15:37.000Z","msg":"假期多客<br />\n出黎做show"},{"pid":"79fe4b34075a45da1a3e46373a0da3d3b399c243","tid":954754,"uid":176063,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T00:17:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"deeb5417e7c17ab4d5774e8e252fc5f7aa83e2d8","tid":954754,"uid":67719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T00:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e393cc00d358a12f7e7d14b06c3c10b58d95a33e","tid":954754,"uid":80199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79fe4b34075a45da1a3e46373a0da3d3b399c243","tid":954754,"uid":176063,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T00:17:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T00:41:43.000Z","msg":"特警搜機場OFFICE, 封埋路"},{"pid":"16a1838b2521a265e0713cafdca965eb6feee762","tid":954754,"uid":89605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T00:51:47.000Z","msg":"係咪有喪屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3100f7a4f288fa6497a862ee6311e81be2231ef","tid":954754,"uid":183270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T00:55:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181225/mobile/bkn-20181225070309283-1225_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181225%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181225070309283-1225_00822_001.html&d=yXiVVfE9H8uuJ1DzMtjeyf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=24fa8ff5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181225/mobile/bkn-20181225070309283-1225_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n今日（25日）凌晨4時許，警方新界南總區交通部特遣隊人員，在青葵公路近長青隧道設置路障進行隨機呼氣測試時，一輛七人車未有停車，加速衝過路障，警員登上警車展開追逐，而七人車高速向機場方向飛馳，直奔青馬大橋，衝過青嶼幹線收費廣場，撞及2個雪糕筒，然後沿北大嶼山公路逃走，期間3輛警車尾隨追截。 <br />\n<br />\n七人車繼續向機場逃走，經過機場南交匯處，直登港珠澳大橋，再折返機場，然後作急掉頭駛上一號客運大樓外。由於交通受阻，七人車失控撞向一輛的士尾部，將其推前撼及一輛客貨車，3輛警車相繼追至，疑收掣不及撞作一團，釀成6車「串燒」。 <br />\n<br />\n七人車年約40至50歲司機慌忙下車逃走，竟由路旁的L8層跳落L4，再由L4跳落L3層逃去無蹤，留下車上一名女子，警員將她拘捕，在車上的軚盤下首飾盒搜獲100克冰毒，以涉嫌偷車及販毒將她扣查。 <br />\n<br />\n在撞車意外中，一名的士司機受傷，另有一名警員追逐涉案司機時，亦跳下L3層跌傷腳部，需一併送院治理，警方仍在現場調查事件。"}]}